Create First Drools Project
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Add Drools Perspective 
----------------------------------------------
Window -> Perspective -> Open Perspective -> Other -> Drools
A drools icon appears on the toolbar with options:
New Drools Project
New Domain Specific Language
New Decistion Table


Create New Drools Project
----------------------------------------------
Drools Icon -> New Drools Project -> "Create a project and populate it "
Project name: hello02
These are filled in:
	User default location
	Build the Project using: Maven
		Group: com.sample
		Artifact ID: hello02
		Version: 1.0.0-SNAPSHOT
	Version: Drools 7.32.0.....
	Select all: 
		Add a sample projects
	Finish
	

We see these project structure:
/hello02
/hello02/src/main/java/com.sample
/hello02/src/main/java/com/sample/DecisionTableTest.java
/hello02/src/main/java/com/sample/DroolsTest.java
/hello02/src/main/java/com/sample/ProcessTest.java
/hello02/src/main/resources
/hello02/src/main/resources/logback-test.xml
/hello02/src/main/resources/com.sample.dtables
/hello02/src/main/resources/com/sample/dtables/Sample.xls
/hello02/src/main/resources/com.sample.process
/hello02/src/main/resources/com/sample/process/sample.bpmn
/hello02/src/main/resources/com.sample.rules
/hello02/src/main/resources/com/sample/rules/Sample.drl
/hello02/src/main/resources/META-INF
/hello02/src/main/resources/META-INF/maven
/hello02/src/main/resources/META-INF/maven/pom.properties
/hello02/src/main/resources/META-INF/kmodule.xml


Change Maven Project 
----------------------------------------------
User the latest Drools/jBPM version. Change the pom.xml
<properties>
	<runtime.version>7.32.0.Final</runtime.version>
</properties>

Update the project:
Run As -> Maven Install
Right click project name: hello2 -> Maven -> Update Project
Right click project name: hello2 -> Refresh


Run DecisionTableTest
----------------------------------------------
Right Click -> DecisionTableTest.java -->Run As -> Java Application
We see  in the console:
	Hello World
	Goodbye cruel world


Run DroolsTest
----------------------------------------------
Right Click -> DroolsTest.java -->Run As -> Java Application
We see  in the console:
	Hello World
	Goodbye cruel world


Run ProcessTest
----------------------------------------------
Right Click -> ProcessTest.java -->Run As -> Java Application
We see  in the console:
	Hello World

	
	
